to replace you.

41:53.598 --> 41:56.557
-  Believe me, I'm not
sticking around to find out.

41:56.601 --> 41:58.820
- What does that mean?

41:58.864 --> 42:00.126
Keri.

42:01.431 --> 42:03.869
I don't care
who has power in the office

42:03.912 --> 42:06.698
